{"tid":1334361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"繁華背後","createTime":"2019-07-20T05:31:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T06:23:21.000Z","uid":171046,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6903d3813af0bcff1687bda0b8bd83f30c474f5e","tid":1334361,"uid":171046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T05:31:35.000Z","msg":"繁華背後，俄羅斯有近300萬貧窮的年輕女性，介乎15至34歲，居於網吧、公園等地方，過著三餐不繼的生活。無國界記者組織拍攝的紀錄片《女性貧困》中，有的因失去家庭經濟之柱，或是父母離異，付不起房租就租住網吧，年紀輕輕已打工為口奔馳。其中一名19歲女生更居於網吧2年多，每天只吃一餐，甚至要與妹妹分吃一個麵包。<br />\n<br />\n據紀錄片《女性貧困》的資料，19歲女生Blake Gkelwnalsva因父親在她年幼時去世，母親肩負家庭和經濟重擔而捱病。Blake初中開始就要在便利店打工，每天早上5點工作至晚上9點，月薪只有3萬盧布（約3,700港元）<br />\n<br />\n另一名19歲女生Eva Gamova，因母親肩負生活費已很吃力，無力為她支付大學學費。為賺取每年50萬盧布（約港元6.1萬）的學費，Eva就從家鄉Ulan-Ude走到Zarechny打工，租住網吧的房間，面積只有一個公廁大。關於將來的去向，Eva坦言不知道。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rhQE1Su.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrhQE1Su.png&h=5f4d6a92&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8483bbc0fd29dbe245d14de2862c35d97debe332","tid":1334361,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T05:32:04.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯有幾「繁華」呀？"},{"pid":"6fe992eb87c5deb3da90f97f5c4f2eae183ac991","tid":1334361,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T05:33:34.000Z","msg":"張相望到都想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f4d922aadff46b072dd4d5ddb7770ec0feddbb","tid":1334361,"uid":171046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T05:42:02.000Z","msg":"CLS"},{"pid":"44ffee9b3c04f9df382b3885b63c8f7d5469148f","tid":1334361,"uid":171046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:08:33.000Z","msg":"少少慘"},{"pid":"4dc9a9cb7c3ab5677b0e8bd1c7ff4503b3967210","tid":1334361,"uid":171046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44ffee9b3c04f9df382b3885b63c8f7d5469148f","tid":1334361,"uid":171046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:08:33.000Z","msg":"少少慘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}